<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Job Match Found!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745 0%, #20c997 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .job-card {
            border: 2px solid #e9ecef;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #ffffff 0%, #f8f9fa 100%);
        }
        .job-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .job-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #212529;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .match-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28a745, #20c997);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            text-align: center;
            min-width: 80px;
        }
        .company-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .company-name {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #495057;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .job-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .detail-icon {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .detail-text {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #495057;
        }
        .requirements-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .requirements-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #212529;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .requirements-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .requirements-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e9ecef;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        .requirements-list li:before {
            content: "‚úì";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
        }
        .skills-section {
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .skills-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .skill-tag {
            background: #e7f3ff;
            color: #0056b3;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            border: 1px solid #b3d7ff;
        }
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
        }
        .secondary-cta {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        .secondary-cta a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        .why-match {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .footer p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .unsubscribe {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #adb5bd;
        }
        .unsubscribe a {
            color: #6c757d;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .job-header {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            .match-badge {
                margin-top: 10px;
                align-self: flex-start;
            }
            .job-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üéØ New Job Match Found!</h1>
            <p>We found a job that matches your profile</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{firstName}},</h2>
            
            <p>Great news! Our AI has found a job opportunity that's a <strong>{{matchScore}}% match</strong> for your profile. Here are the details:</p>
            
            <div class="job-card">
                <div class="job-header">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="job-title">{{jobTitle}}</h3>
                        <div class="company-info">
                            <span class="company-name">{{companyName}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="match-badge">{{matchScore}}% Match</div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="job-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-icon">üìç</span>
                        <span class="detail-text">{{jobLocation}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-icon">üíº</span>
                        <span class="detail-text">{{capitalize employmentType}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-icon">üè†</span>
                        <span class="detail-text">{{capitalize workMode}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{#if salary}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-icon">üí∞</span>
                        <span class="detail-text">{{salary}}</span>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <span class="detail-icon">üìÖ</span>
                        <span class="detail-text">Posted {{formatDate postedDate}}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                {{#if requirements}}
                <div class="requirements-section">
                    <div class="requirements-title">Key Requirements:</div>
                    <ul class="requirements-list">
                        {{#each (first requirements 5)}}
                        <li>{{this}}</li>
                        {{/each}}
                    </ul>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
                
                {{#if skills}}
                <div class="skills-section">
                    <div class="requirements-title">Required Skills:</div>
                    <div class="skills-container">
                        {{#each (first skills 10)}}
                        <span class="skill-tag">{{this}}</span>
                        {{/each}}
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{/if}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="why-match">
                <h4>ü§ñ Why is this a good match?</h4>
                <p>Our AI analyzed your profile and found strong alignment with this role based on your skills, experience, and preferences. The {{matchScore}}% match score indicates excellent compatibility!</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{jobUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Job Details & Apply</a>
                <div class="secondary-cta">
                    <p>Or <a href="{{jobUrl}}">click here</a> to view the full job description</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <h3>üí° Quick Tips:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Review the job requirements carefully</li>
                <li>Tailor your resume for this specific role</li>
                <li>Research the company before applying</li>
                <li>Prepare a compelling cover letter</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>Good luck with your application! We're here to help you land your dream job.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Resume Refresh Platform</strong></p>
            <p>AI-powered job matching for your career success</p>
            <p>Need help? Contact us at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}" class="support-link">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            
            <div class="unsubscribe">
                <p>Don't want job match notifications? <a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe here</a></p>
                <p>You can also manage your notification preferences in your <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}/settings">account settings</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
